---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Lighthouse Mentoring - Craig Fearn"
  description="Privacy policy for Lighthouse Mentoring - how we collect, use and protect your personal information when you use our consulting and advisory services.">

  <!-- Privacy Policy Hero -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-hero mb-6 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 text-center">
        Your privacy matters. Here's how we protect your personal information.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 text-center mt-4">
        Last updated: January 2025
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy Content -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl prose prose-lg mx-auto">

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact us for consultations or inquiries</li>
        <li>Book strategic assessment sessions</li>
        <li>Subscribe to our insights or updates</li>
        <li>Engage our board advisory or coaching services</li>
      </ul>

      <p>This may include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Name, email address, and contact information</li>
        <li>Professional details and company information</li>
        <li>Communication preferences</li>
        <li>Information about your business challenges and requirements</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide consulting, advisory, and coaching services</li>
        <li>Respond to your inquiries and requests</li>
        <li>Schedule and conduct strategic assessments</li>
        <li>Send relevant business insights and updates (with your consent)</li>
        <li>Improve our services and understand client needs</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information only in these limited circumstances:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>With trusted service providers who assist in delivering our services</li>
        <li>When required by law or to protect our rights</li>
        <li>With your explicit consent</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. This includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Encrypted data transmission</li>
        <li>Secure data storage systems</li>
        <li>Limited access to personal information</li>
        <li>Regular security assessments</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Under GDPR and UK data protection laws, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access your personal information</li>
        <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
        <li>Data portability</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
      <p>Our website may use cookies and analytics tools to improve your experience and understand how our site is used. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>7. Retention Period</h2>
      <p>We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to provide our services and fulfill legal obligations. Client engagement data is typically retained for 7 years in accordance with professional standards.</p>

      <h2>8. International Transfers</h2>
      <p>Your data is primarily processed within the UK. Any international transfers are subject to appropriate safeguards under GDPR.</p>

      <h2>9. Updates to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy periodically. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated policy on our website.</p>

      <h2>10. Contact Information</h2>
      <p>For questions about this privacy policy or to exercise your data rights, contact:</p>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg not-prose">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-2">Craig Fearn - Data Controller</p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:craig.fearn@lighthousementoring.co.uk" class="text-primary hover:underline">craig.fearn@lighthousementoring.co.uk</a></p>
        <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+447738419446" class="text-primary hover:underline">+44 7738 419446</a></p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Lighthouse Mentoring operates as a sole proprietorship under UK law.
          <br>Craig Fearn FCMI, FRSPH - IoD Ambassador
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>